CustomField.description: Amount outstanding based on the following formula: (Amount) - (Amended Amount) - (Waived Amount) - (Paid Amount).
CustomField.formula: If(MUSW__Amount__c - MUSW__Amount_Waived__c - MUSW__Amount_Paid__c - MUSW__Amended_Amount__c < 0, 0, MUSW__Amount__c - MUSW__Amount_Waived__c - MUSW__Amount_Paid__c - MUSW__Amended_Amount__c)
CustomField.label: Outstanding
